#message:02:000
{
	[Style Right]
	I look away for like five seconds[BR]
	and some stupid Shy Guy comes[BR]
	and takes over the till.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	What the heck is up with that?[Wait][End]
}

#message:02:001
{
	[Style Right]
	Hey wassup?[BR]
	[Pause 10]It's me, the legendary Shy Guy.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I won't sell anything to a[BR]
	smelly junkie like you![BR]
	[Pause 10][Wave]Ha![Pause 3] No way![/fx][Wait][End]
}

#message:02:002
{
	[Style Right]
	[Wave]Dang... busted...[Wait][End]
}

#message:02:003
{
	[Style Right]
	Hey, thanks for getting that[BR]
	stupid Shy Guy outta here.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Now I continue my dad's legacy[BR]
	and it's all thanks to you![BR]
	[Pause 10]Buy some stuff,[Pause 5] it's on the[BR]
	house, alright?[Wait][End]
}

#message:02:004
{
	[Style Right]
	Greetings, my friend.[BR]
	[Pause 10]I don't believe I've seen you[BR]
	around town, so you must be[BR]
	a newbie.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Either you're new around here[BR]
	or you're a seasoned veteran,[BR]
	perhaps I can spread some[BR]
	knowledge around.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Any bits of info can be great[BR]
	to get the brain juices going.[BR]
	[Pause 15]Speak to me if you'd like[BR]
	to know more.[Wait][End]
}

#message:02:005
{
	[Style Right]
	Ah, you'd like to know some[BR]
	nifty information, is that[BR]
	right?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Well don't worry,[Pause 3] I don't charge[BR]
	hundreds of coins like those[BR]
	other scummy salesmen.[BR]
