}

#message:02:00E
{
	[Style Right]
	What a weird sheet you've[BR]
	got in your hands.[BR]
	[Pause 10]It's a manuscript? [Pause 10]No,[Pause 5] it's not.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Blimey. Well this is a strange[BR]
	paper, truly.[BR]
